"Passphrase (leave blank if none)" = "口令(没有则留空)";
"Passphrase is in your macOS Keychain." = "口令保存在您的 macOS 钥匙串中。";
"Passphrases (if any) are stored in the macOS Keychain — bromure-ac fetches via SSH_ASKPASS at session launch and never logs the value." = "口令（如有）保存在 macOS 钥匙串中 — bromure-ac 在会话启动时通过 SSH_ASKPASS 获取，绝不会记录该值。";
"Password / token" = "密码 / 令牌";
"Paste this into github.com/settings/keys (or your hosting provider's equivalent). The matching private key lives only inside this profile." = "将此粘贴到 github.com/settings/keys（或您的托管商对应页面）。对应的私钥仅存在于该配置文件内。";
"Personal access token from cloud.digitalocean.com → API → Generate New Token. Injected into the VM as `DIGITALOCEAN_ACCESS_TOKEN` env + `~/.config/doctl/config.yaml` — `doctl auth init` is unnecessary, you're already logged in." = "来自 cloud.digitalocean.com → API → Generate New Token 的个人访问令牌。会作为 `DIGITALOCEAN_ACCESS_TOKEN` 环境变量并写入 `~/.config/doctl/config.yaml` 注入到虚拟机中 — 无需再执行 `doctl auth init`，您已登录。";
"Personal access tokens for git over HTTPS. Stored encrypted on the host; the proxy swaps them onto outbound requests so the VM only ever holds the fake. `gh` and `glab` pick up GH_TOKEN / GITLAB_TOKEN env automatically." = "用于通过 HTTPS 访问 git 的个人访问令牌。在主机上加密存储；代理在出站请求时进行替换，因此虚拟机只持有伪造的令牌。`gh` 与 `glab` 会自动读取 GH_TOKEN / GITLAB_TOKEN 环境变量。";
"Point bromure at any existing SSH private key (RSA, ed25519, ecdsa) — encrypted ones included. The key is loaded into the per-profile bromure ssh-agent at every session launch; passphrases are stored in the macOS Keychain." = "将 bromure 指向任意现有的 SSH 私钥（RSA、ed25519、ecdsa — 加密的也支持）。每次会话启动时密钥会加载到该配置文件专属的 bromure ssh-agent；口令保存在 macOS 钥匙串中。";
