"Session trace" = "会话跟踪";
"Sessions running under this profile normally stream metadata (tools, files, commands, token usage) to your workspace. Turn this on to keep this profile's activity local — neither the title-bar indicator nor the admin's session list will see anything from this profile. The local trace inspector is unaffected." = "在该配置文件下运行的会话通常会将元数据（工具、文件、命令、令牌用量）流式发送到您的工作区。启用此项可将该配置文件的活动保留在本地 — 标题栏指示器和管理员的会话列表都将看不到该配置文件的任何信息。本地跟踪检查器不受影响。";
"Storage controls only apply to real profiles. They appear in each profile's editor when you create or edit one." = "存储控制仅对实际配置文件生效。在您创建或编辑配置文件时会显示在该配置文件的编辑器中。";
