/* Guardrails */
"Guardrails" = "防护栏";
"Guardrails strips destructive operations from the protocols this agent speaks. It's enforced on the host — inside the proxy — so a misbehaving or compromised agent in the VM can't bypass it. Blocked calls return a hard error the agent sees." = "防护栏会从该智能体所使用的协议中剥离破坏性操作。它在主机端（代理内部）强制执行，因此 VM 中行为异常或被入侵的智能体无法绕过。被阻止的调用会向智能体返回一个明确的错误。";
"Databases" = "数据库";
"No database endpoints configured. Add MongoDB, ClickHouse, or Elasticsearch endpoints under Credentials to guard them here." = "未配置数据库端点。请在“凭据”中添加 MongoDB、ClickHouse 或 Elasticsearch 端点以在此处加以防护。";
"No kubeconfigs on this profile — add one under Credentials for this to take effect." = "此配置文件没有 kubeconfig — 请在“凭据”中添加一个以使其生效。";
"No registries on this profile — add one under Credentials for this to take effect." = "此配置文件没有镜像仓库 — 请在“凭据”中添加一个以使其生效。";
"Set this endpoint's host under Credentials for the guard to take effect." = "请在“凭据”中设置此端点的主机，以使防护生效。";
"Off" = "关闭";
"Block destructive" = "阻止破坏性操作";
"Read-only" = "只读";
"No filtering." = "不过滤。";
"Block deletes/drops; allow creates and updates." = "阻止删除/drop；允许创建和更新。";
"Block every change; reads only." = "阻止所有更改；仅允许读取。";
"Applies to the kube API servers from this profile's kubeconfigs (e.g. `kubectl delete` fails cleanly)." = "适用于此配置文件 kubeconfig 中的 kube API 服务器（例如 `kubectl delete` 会干净地失败）。";
"All *.amazonaws.com APIs; classified by action name (Delete*/Terminate* = destructive, Get*/List*/Describe* = read)." = "所有 *.amazonaws.com API；按操作名称分类（Delete*/Terminate* = 破坏性，Get*/List*/Describe* = 读取）。";
"api.digitalocean.com — DELETE = destructive." = "api.digitalocean.com — DELETE = 破坏性。";
"Registries you've added under Credentials — pull = read, push = write, delete = destructive." = "你在“凭据”中添加的镜像仓库 — pull = 读取，push = 写入，delete = 破坏性。";
"github.com REST API + git over HTTPS; read-only also blocks `git push`." = "github.com REST API 与基于 HTTPS 的 git；只读模式还会阻止 `git push`。";
"gitlab.com REST API + git over HTTPS." = "gitlab.com REST API 与基于 HTTPS 的 git。";
