"Bromure scans the agent's AI traffic on-device for injected instructions — nothing leaves the Mac. Each detector uses a local model, downloaded from bromure.io the first time you enable it." = "Bromure 在本机分析代理的 AI 流量以检测被注入的指令——任何数据都不会离开 Mac。每个检测器使用本地模型，首次启用时从 bromure.io 下载。";
"Scores the file contents, web pages, and tool output the agent reads (Prompt Guard). Catches “ignore previous instructions / exfiltrate secrets” hidden in a rogue repository. Downloads ~272 MB on first enable." = "对代理读取的文件内容、网页和工具输出进行评分（Prompt Guard），捕捉藏在恶意仓库中的「忽略先前指令 / 窃取机密」。首次启用时下载约 272 MB。";
"Scores CLAUDE.md, AGENTS.md, GROK.md, and the other instruction / settings files Claude Code, Codex, and Grok load as authority. Downloads ~571 MB on first enable." = "对 Claude Code、Codex 和 Grok 作为权威加载的 CLAUDE.md、AGENTS.md、GROK.md 及其他指令 / 设置文件进行评分。首次启用时下载约 571 MB。";
"“Log but continue” records detections to the Security Log window. “Ask me what to do” pauses the request and shows the flagged text. “Block” fails the request outright." = "“记录但继续”将检测记录到安全日志窗口。“询问我该怎么做”会暂停请求并显示被标记的文本。“阻止”会直接让请求失败。";
